I"­<p>Helping is important in life. You help the weak to get stronger, you help the hungry to learn fishing, you help someone to achieve her goals. Why not help your compiler to perform some optimization? As always, help benefits both the one that helps and the one that received a hand.</p>

<p>A good way to help the C++ compiler is to declare whatever variable const that should not change. It requires little effort, right?</p>
